{"tid":1528853,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"如果罷課係冇人知嘅、 冇做成影響嘅，咁罷黎做乜","createTime":"2019-09-01T15:21:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T02:51:06.000Z","uid":100847,"like":41,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"36bbf4f44dee115ed74343d5a54545af41209cdb","tid":1528853,"uid":100847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T15:21:26.000Z","msg":"回帶<br />\n仲記得五年前<br />\n大家號召罷課時一心想做返啲野<br />\n有連續幾日坐喺圖書館所謂自修<br />\n<br />\n嗰陣得嗰零丁幾人罷課<br />\n仲只準坐喺圖書館<br />\n唔講根本冇同學老師知<br />\n而家諗返起真係覺得自己好廢好天真<br />\n乜都冇做<br />\n行出圖書館都覺得慚愧<br />\n咁罷法莫講話港共政權<br />\n連出面落街買餸嘅師奶都唔會知<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我想講<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">如果罷課係冇人知嘅、<br />\n冇做成影響嘅<br />\n咁罷黎做乜</span><br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n就算留喺學校唔出去行動<br />\n都仲可以有好多作為<br />\n連儂牆、大字報、默站、靜坐、戴口罩、小息論壇講香港歷史社會議題順便溫歷史通識......<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人咁有創意<br />\n大把橋可以走校規罅<br />\n要引起其他同學關注討論繼而拉攏、參與、行動<br />\n愈多人就愈多關注<br />\n先有贏嘅機會<br />\n<br />\n唔好真係諗住離開左自己班房去左第二間房自修<br />\n件事就會自動修正<br />\n一係唔好做搏等攬炒 一決定做就做好佢好唔好<br />\n<br />\n多謝咁多位睇到呢度嘅巴絲<br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山 各自努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7576f426f92565dd36549771a04626c94c87ff6b","tid":1528853,"uid":6953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T15:21:54.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"c2682e0bd2ad04c68df907c5d84770032f90faf9","tid":1528853,"uid":259345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T15:22:13.000Z","msg":"我忍左佢好撚耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一句講晒 聽日麻包袋藍絲副校長 割唔割<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1528684\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1528684</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"dc6c764e5fc5c54c6f0f58a6ca63cfcbb311ebb3","tid":1528853,"uid":100847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T15:22:43.000Z","msg":"自推十次"},{"pid":"74d22aad98b855d7ac22564419ab0509b399bc18","tid":1528853,"uid":100847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T15:23:01.000Z","msg":"九"},{"pid":"060955cd5985005da9a0474332c98be9ea5c090f","tid":1528853,"uid":100847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T15:23:14.000Z","msg":"八"},{"pid":"b0410b3933127f43118d44160c07429c05a67378","tid":1528853,"uid":100847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T15:23:24.000Z","msg":"七"},{"pid":"cee3ce3b9bc366abd4fa90db5f5818b24e98b582","tid":1528853,"uid":100847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T15:23:34.000Z","msg":"六"},{"pid":"2b16834ad95b3e0787ac4426b6ce78c8e100f646","tid":1528853,"uid":100847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T15:23:46.000Z","msg":"五"},{"pid":"8d555eee487a6d03a4d412bad50cd1560995dc32","tid":1528853,"uid":100847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T15:24:06.000Z","msg":"四"},{"pid":"38aa2eac248adbd20e34413b52700ee2e439190a","tid":1528853,"uid":303538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T15:24:16.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"0651ec5ce9eccfdb51d1aeaaac0dc01878119951","tid":1528853,"uid":100847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T15:24:18.000Z","msg":"三"},{"pid":"759f9b9bf2045d7b28a0027db4eef1e7bd184e1b","tid":1528853,"uid":100847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T15:24:29.000Z","msg":"二"},{"pid":"2c6ba81a23e8f17a1c118493c6b23a0435c3f64d","tid":1528853,"uid":100847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T15:24:40.000Z","msg":"一"},{"pid":"5a783cf439c4686b88aab656c778c216cc78f6e0","tid":1528853,"uid":100847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T15:25:40.000Z","msg":"唔記得咗P牌仔推post係推唔郁嘅添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj